title: Honduras again halts release of vote count in presidential election as centrist Nasralla holds narrow lead
description: TEGUCIGALPA, Dec 3 (Reuters) - Honduras again halted the publication of official results in its presidential election, an electoral official said on Wednesday, as centrist Salvador Nasralla maintained a narrow lead ahead of Trump-backed conservative Nasry Asf…
